In High Street and in Station Road on Saturday the 8th of June 1985, 25 people were asked whether they would prefer to ride a bike or use a car in the Carnoustie area.Here is a table of the results:
NUMBER : 2 4 6 8 10 12 14 16 CYCLES :{ |||||||||||||||| CARS :{ |||||||||||}
Bicycles were chosen because they cost less to run.Only 4 of the people spoken to did not have bicycles.On the other hand,only 2 of the people asked did not have cars.Cars were chosen because travelling was quicker. Many of the people who chose to use bikes said that bikes didn't cause air pollution.This is something that people should think about in future.
